-Hey.

38
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,472
No, you're just in time.

39
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,039
Thanks.

40
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,597
Hey, come on. We can squeeze you in.

41
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:01,555
-It's okay. I'm gonna see you later.
-Oh, no, no, no. Where are you going?

42
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,312
To get what I want.

43
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,880
"Husband seeking to satisfy
wife's curiosity.

44
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:46,350
Enjoys tall--" Careful.

45
