Yeah, I know.

126
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:23,233
But other than that, he's great.
You should call him.

127
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:26,949
And say what? "Hi. It's your illegitimate
daughter. Wanna have lunch? "

128
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:31,552
-You could have Kirsten ask him for you.
-Yeah, she has. Couple times.

129
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:36,712
So he'll call, right? I mean--
I mean, he's got to, sooner or later.

130
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,950
Yeah, right, sooner or later.

131
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:49,359
At the moment, this is
the only beach-adjacent property...

132
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,988
...we have in your price range,
Mr. Cohen.

133
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:54,871
As you can see,
it's a bit of a fixer-upper.

134
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,434
That's one way to put it.

135
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:59,910
Who are you kidding, Gail?
This place is a first-class dump.

136
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,552
And I like it.

137
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,994
Sandy, no, you don't.

138
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:06,754
